<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>7.3 Liter Diesel Engine Diagnostics (1991) - "SOLID STATE" GLOW PLUG ANALYSIS GUIDE - "SOLID STATE" GLOW
        PLUG SYSTEM REPLACEMENT PROCEDURES - REASSEMBLY (Harness Assembly)
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="proctype" graphiccount="2">
        <title>REASSEMBLY (Harness Assembly)</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install a new or repaired harness as required. Route the harness as shown in Figures
                <hotlnk xrefid="ef4600642">6.42</hotlnk>
                or
                <hotlnk xrefid="ef4600643">6.43</hotlnk>.
            </para>
            <specpara>
                <note>
                    <para>Harness must be under the injection lines on both sides of the engine.</para>
                </note>
            </specpara>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Bolt control unit onto the intake manifold. Tighten bolts to a standard torque of 7 lbf-ft.
                (10 Nm) using a calibrated torque wrench. DO NOT OVERTIGHTEN TO PREVENT CONTROL UNIT HOUSING DAMAGE.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install the ground ring terminal and harness clamp arranging the washers and nuts as
                depicted in Figure
                <hotlnk document="e460_69.xml" xrefid="ef4600640">6.40</hotlnk>.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Reconnect the following connectors: (Figures
                <hotlnk xrefid="ef4600642">6.42</hotlnk>
                and
                <hotlnk xrefid="ef4600643">6.43</hotlnk>.)
            </para>
            <randlist type="bullet">
                <item>
                    <para>Electric shut-off.</para>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <para>Housing pressure cold advance.</para>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <para>Cold idle solenoid.</para>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <para>Glow plugs.</para>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <para>HPCA coolant temperature sensor.</para>
                </item>
            </randlist>
            <figure id="ef4600642" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="cg11760" filename="../figcg1/CG11760.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 6.42 Glow Plug Harness Routing and Connector Locations [1988 Model Year Engines and
                    prior shown]
                </caption>
            </figure>
            <figure id="ef4600643" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="cg15003" filename="../figcg1/CG15003.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 6.43 Glow Plug Harness Routing and Connector Locations [1989 Model Year Engines and
                    beyond shown]
                </caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
